#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:17
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"Casts light in a 2D environment. Light is defined by a (usually "
"grayscale) texture, a color, an energy value, a mode (see constants), and"
" various other parameters (range and shadows-related)."
msgstr "在2D环境中投射光线。灯光由一个（通常灰度）材质、一个颜色、一个能量值、一个模式（参见常数）、以及各种其他参数（范围和阴影相关的）所定义。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:21
msgid "**Note:** Light2D can also be used as a mask."
msgstr "**注意**：Light2D也可以用作遮罩。"

