#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:86
msgid "enum **Mode**:"
msgstr "枚举 **Mode**："

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:88
msgid ""
"**MODE_ADD** = **0** --- Adds the value of pixels corresponding to the "
"Light2D to the values of pixels under it. This is the common behavior of "
"a light."
msgstr "**MODE_ADD** = **0** —— 将与Light2D对应的像素值，添加到其下方的像素值。这是灯光的一般行为。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:90
msgid ""
"**MODE_SUB** = **1** --- Subtracts the value of pixels corresponding to "
"the Light2D to the values of pixels under it, resulting in inversed light"
" effect."
msgstr "**MODE_SUB** = **1** —— 将与Light2D对应的像素值，减去其下的像素值，从而产生逆光效果。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:92
msgid ""
"**MODE_MIX** = **2** --- Mix the value of pixels corresponding to the "
"Light2D to the values of pixels under it by linear interpolation."
msgstr "**MODE_MIX** = **2** —— 通过线性插值，将与Light2D对应的像素值，与其下的像素值混合。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:94
msgid ""
"**MODE_MASK** = **3** --- The light texture of the Light2D is used as a "
"mask, hiding or revealing parts of the screen underneath depending on the"
" value of each pixel of the light (mask) texture."
msgstr "**MODE_MASK** = **3** —— Light2D的光照纹理用作蒙版，根据光照（蒙版）纹理的每个像素的值，隐藏或显示屏幕下方的部分。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:106
msgid "enum **ShadowFilter**:"
msgstr "枚举 **ShadowFilter**："

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:108
msgid ""
"**SHADOW_FILTER_NONE** = **0** --- No filter applies to the shadow map. "
"See :ref:`shadow_filter <class_Light2D_property_shadow_filter>`."
msgstr ""
"**SHADOW_FILTER_NONE** = **0** —— 没有过滤器应用于阴影贴图。参见 :ref:`shadow_filter "
"<class_Light2D_property_shadow_filter>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:110
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**SHADOW_FILTER_PCF5** = **1** --- Percentage closer filtering (5 "
"samples) applies to the shadow map. See :ref:`shadow_filter "
"<class_Light2D_property_shadow_filter>`."
msgstr ""
"**SHADOW_FILTER_PCF5** = **2** —— 百分比相近滤波（5个样本）应用于阴影贴图。参见 "
":ref:`shadow_filter <class_Light2D_property_shadow_filter>`。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_light2d.rst:112
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**SHADOW_FILTER_PCF13** = **2** --- Percentage closer filtering (13 "
"samples) applies to the shadow map. See :ref:`shadow_filter "
"<class_Light2D_property_shadow_filter>`."
msgstr ""
"**SHADOW_FILTER_PCF13** = **5** —— 百分比相近滤波（13个样本）应用于阴影贴图。参见 "
":ref:`shadow_filter <class_Light2D_property_shadow_filter>`。"

